headline: MetLife Increases Common Stock Dividend by 4.1%
summary: NEW YORK, April 22, 2025--MetLife, Inc. (NYSE: MET) today announced that its board of directors has declared a second quarter 2025 common stock dividend of $0.5675 per share, an increase of 4.1% from the first quarter common stock dividend of $0.545 per share. MetLife has increased its common stock quarterly dividend at a 9.0% compound annual growth rate since 2011.
